<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Dec1932"><font color="red">27 December 1932</font> <i>NLPK</i> (Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): I am still waiting for the proofs of the new fragment which have not reached me yet &hellip; You can absolutely reassure your brother and Huebsch since all the fragments published up to now i.e. ALP, HCE, the <i>Two Tales</i> and the new one will constitute in all not more than a hundred pages and this is about one twentieth of the entire book </div>
